\par <#/>According to reports landing on my desk, a Hong Kong businessman, K.K. Poon is willing to buy all the cattle gallstones you can supply. <#/>The gallstones the businessman is after are found inside the gall bladder (a small sac attached to the li
ver) and are needed for research projects.
