\par <#/>Even if the man could not raise the dowry, he is not like that patient who has missed money to pay for his hospital bills. <#/>Marriage is n
ot an incidental and accidental affair so even if someone does not have enough resources, then he should not make an attempt to marry at all and in the process call a <ea/>Harambee for it.
